    "whatItDoes": "Full Sentry SDK setup for Ruby. Use when asked to add Sentry to Ruby, install sentry-ruby, setup Sentry in Rails/Sinatra/Rack, or configure error monitoring, tracing, logging, metrics, profiling, or crons for Ruby applications. Also handles migration from AppSignal, Honeybadger, Bugsnag, Rollbar, or Airbrake. Supports Rails, Sinatra, Rack, Sidekiq, and Resque.",
